{"id":"https://doi.org/10.54900/fnj5mz2-2g0bj5m","title":"Preprint as a Way to Universal Open Access","link":"https://doi.org/10.54900/fnj5mz2-2g0bj5m","published":"2022-09-28T09:31:06.000+00:00","description":"A journey started with the INArxiv hosted by The Center of Open Science to RINarxiv hosted by BRIN Indonesia.Current situation in academia (especially in Global South). It’s very hard for us to keep our heads...","isPermalink":true,"tags":[],"authors":[{"name":"Dasapta Erwin Irawan","url":"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1526-0863"}],"image":"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/Screenshot-2022-09-19-at-17.14.26.png","modified":"2023-01-12T19:26:10.000+00:00","contentHtml":" <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/1-Universal-open-access-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/1-Universal-open-access-3.png 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/1-Universal-open-access-3.png 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>A journey started with the INArxiv hosted by The Center of Open Science to RINarxiv hosted by BRIN Indonesia.</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/2-Universal-open-access-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/2-Universal-open-access-3.png 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/2-Universal-open-access-3.png 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Current situation in academia (especially in Global South). It’s very hard for us to keep our heads above water.</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/3-Universal-open-access-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/3-Universal-open-access-3.png 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/3-Universal-open-access-3.png 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>The basic ingredients of preprinting are: ethics, integrity, and norms. We have a generic set of values and also subject-specific and culture-specific values.</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/4-Universal-open-access-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/4-Universal-open-access-3.png 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/4-Universal-open-access-3.png 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Part 1: Universal open access for authors. No matter which journal you submit your manuscript to, make sure to self-archive the preprint and postprint version to take back your freedom to write, to share, and to retain copyrights.</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/5-Universal-open-access-4.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/5-Universal-open-access-4.png 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/5-Universal-open-access-4.png 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Part 2: Universal open access for readers. Preprints ship out the rights to search, to read, and to reuse to the readers.</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/6-Universal-open-access-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/6-Universal-open-access-3.png 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/6-Universal-open-access-3.png 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>To achieve both parts, preprint servers or repositories needed to be kept non-profit or as part of governmental infrastructure.</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/7-Universal-open-access-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/7-Universal-open-access-3.png 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/7-Universal-open-access-3.png 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>In the end …How can we create positive dents in the community?</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/Universal-open-access.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/Universal-open-access.jpeg 600w, https://upstream.force11.org/content/images/2022/09/Universal-open-access.jpeg 960w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>All together!</figcaption></figure> "}